---
import ImageComp from "./ImageComp.astro";

const simImage = "/src/assets/flight-simulator-la-flight-academy-los-angeles-van-nuys-gleim-batd-3.jpg";
const simAlt = "Gleim BATD Flight Simulator in use at LA Flight Academy";
---

<section class="bg-white pt-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto flex flex-col gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center justify-center w-full">
      <div>
        <ImageComp
          imagePath={simImage}
          imageAlt={simAlt}
          styles="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover"
          widths={[240, 540, 720, 1080, 1440, 1980]}
          sizes={`(max-width: 300px) 240px, (max-width: 660px) 540px, (max-width: 900px) 720px, (max-width: 1200px) 1080px, (max-width: 1800px) 1440px, 1920px`}    
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Train Smarter with Our FAA-Approved Flight Simulator</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          LA Flight Academy offers a <strong>Gleim BATD Flight Simulator</strong> at our Van Nuys, California location — an affordable, flexible tool that supports both new and experienced pilots. It’s FAA-approved for use in Part 61 training programs and can be logged for specific flight hour credit.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 mb-6 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Private Pilot:</strong> Log up to 2.5 hours toward your PPL under 14 CFR §61.109(k)(1)</li>
          <li><strong>Instrument Rating:</strong> Log up to 10 hours under 14 CFR §61.65(i)</li>
          <li><strong>Instrument Currency:</strong> Stay current per 14 CFR §61.57(c)</li>
          <li><strong>Affordable Rates:</strong> $70/hour or $60/hour with block rate</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Whether you're working toward your <strong>private pilot license</strong>, preparing for your <strong>instrument checkride</strong>, or maintaining <strong>IFR currency</strong>, the simulator provides a reliable and efficient training environment right here in Los Angeles.
        </p>
      </div>  
    </div>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary mt-6 w-full md:w-auto">
      Contact Us to Schedule Your Simulator Session </a>
  </div>
</section>
